How to install tensorflow on mac?

REF
- https://github.com/jeffheaton/t81_558_deep_learning/blob/master/install/tensorflow-install-mac-metal-jul-2021.ipynb
- https://developer.apple.com/metal/tensorflow-plugin/

HOW TO?
chmod +x ~/Downloads/Miniforge3-MacOSX-arm64.sh
sh ~/Downloads/Miniforge3-MacOSX-arm64.sh
source ~/miniforge3/bin/activate
reopen terminal
conda config --set auto_activate_base False
reopen terminal
export GRPC_PYTHON_BUILD_SYSTEM_OPENSSL=1
export GRPC_PYTHON_BUILD_SYSTEM_ZLIB=1
conda env create -f dep.yml -n batman 
conda activate batman
